fields.fullDescription: The F+ F170L mobile phone has a 1.77-inch TFT color screen. The keys are large and backlit. The resolution is 160x128 pixels. The SC8955 processor is at the core of the phone. The built-in and RAM memory is 32 MB each. There are slots for installing two SIM cards. The 2G standard is supported in wireless networks. The case type is a monoblock, the material is plastic. There is a built-in flashlight.  The phone has an FM receiver, vibration alert, and alarm clock. You can set MP3 as a ringtone. During a conversation, you can switch to speakerphone mode. It is possible to install a microSDHC memory card - up to 32 GB.  The organizer is represented by a calendar, calculator, date / time. Connectors - microUSB and 3.5 mm for connecting a headset. The power source is a lithium-ion battery with a capacity of 600 mAh. Time
